name.pehl.piriti.rebind.fieldhandler
Class FieldContext

java.lang.Object
  name.pehl.piriti.rebind.fieldhandler.FieldContext

public class FieldContext
extends Object

Class which contains information needed to generate code for the evaluation, conversion and assignment of a field. An instance of this class is passed to the FieldHandler.
